---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation:
-------------

Required: 
- Python 2.5 or higher 
- Numerical Python or its successor NumPy
- ScientificPython 2.7 or higher
- pymmLib (http://pymmlib.sourceforge.net/) if reading mmCIF files
  is required

CDTK will use Numeric or NumPy depending on how ScientificPython has been
configured.

Installation is as simple as

    python setup.py build
    python setup.py install

(the second command requires root privileges on many installations).
